andidate\u202fB is the only one with explicit evidence of both (100\u202f% reliability and calm in crisis). While his interpersonal style is a drawback, the safety\u2011critical attributes outweigh the crew\u2011interaction concerns compared with the other candidates, who either lack proven calmness/reliability or have more severe teamwork deficits.\nI would therefore **favor Candidate\u202fB**, pending any additional data on A\u2019s pressure handling or D\u2019s crew\u2011cooperation that might shift the balance.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_3\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
