ndidates\u202fA and\u202fD lack any data on calmness under pressure or concrete crew\u2011cooperation outcomes, which are critical gaps. Candidate\u202fC, although reliable and stress\u2011resilient, has clear communication and attitude weaknesses that could directly impair crew coordination on long\u2011haul operations.\n**Therefore, based on the available evidence, I continue to favor Candidate\u202fB as the best overall fit for the long\u2011distance pilot role, while remaining open to any new concrete information that might shift this assessment.**\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
